name: weather_forecaster
title: Meteorological Prediction Engine
description: Generates localized weather forecasts using real-time sensor data and historical patterns. Optimized for agricultural and urban planning use cases.
input: current_weather_data: dict[str, float], historical_weather_data: list[dict], location: str
output: forecast_period: str, temperature_range: dict[str, float], weather_conditions: list[str], confidence_score: float

name: stock_analyst
title: Financial Market Prediction System
description: Analyzes equity patterns and market indicators to predict short-term stock movements. Supports portfolio optimization strategies.
input: stock_symbols: list[str], historical_prices: dict[str, list[float]], market_indicators: dict[str, float]
output: predicted_trends: dict[str, str], risk_level: Literal['low', 'medium', 'high'], price_targets: dict[str, float]

name: social_media_monitor
title: Social Listening Analyzer
description: Tracks brand sentiment and emerging trends across major platforms using NLP and network analysis techniques.
input: raw_posts: list[str], platform: Literal['twitter', 'facebook', 'instagram'], time_window: str
output: sentiment_distribution: dict[str, float], trending_topics: list[str], influencer_mentions: list[str]

name: ecommerce_recommender
title: Personalized Shopping Assistant
description: Generates hyper-personalized product suggestions using collaborative filtering and basket analysis algorithms.
input: user_purchase_history: list[dict], product_catalog: list[dict], browsing_behavior: dict[str, list]
output: personalized_recommendations: list[str], cross_sell_opportunities: list[str], discount_suggestions: list[str]

name: medical_triage
title: Clinical Symptom Evaluator
description: Prioritizes patient care using vital sign analysis and symptom pattern recognition. Complies with ER triage protocols.
input: patient_vitals: dict[str, float], reported_symptoms: list[str], medical_history: dict
output: urgency_level: Literal['emergency', 'urgent', 'non-urgent'], probable_diagnoses: list[str], next_steps: list[str]

name: legal_document_parser
title: Contractual Clause Identifier
description: Extracts critical legal obligations and risks from complex agreements using legal NLP frameworks.
input: legal_text: str, jurisdiction: str, document_type: Literal['contract', 'nda', 'patent']
output: key_clauses: list[str], obligations: list[str], expiration_dates: list[str], risks: list[str]

name: supply_chain_optimizer
title: Inventory Optimization Engine
description: Balances stock levels and logistics routes using constraint programming and demand forecasting models.
input: inventory_levels: dict[str, float], demand_forecast: dict[str, float], supplier_lead_times: dict[str, int]
output: reorder_points: dict[str, int], optimal_routes: dict[str, list], cost_reduction_areas: list[str]

name: content_moderator
title: Community Safety Filter
description: Automates content policy enforcement using multi-modal analysis and reputation-based scoring systems.
input: user_content: str, community_guidelines: dict[str, list], user_reputation_score: float
output: violation_types: list[str], moderation_action: Literal['approve', 'flag', 'remove'], confidence_level: float

name: energy_consumption_analyst
title: Power Usage Optimizer
description: Identifies energy waste patterns and suggests efficiency improvements using IoT sensor analytics.
input: smart_meter_data: list[float], appliance_list: list[str], time_frame: str
output: peak_usage_times: list[str], inefficient_devices: list[str], cost_saving_tips: list[str]

name: crypto_market_analyzer
title: Blockchain Trend Detector
description: Monitors cryptocurrency markets for emerging opportunities and security risks using on-chain analytics.
input: blockchain_data: list[dict], exchange_volumes: dict[str, float], market_sentiment: dict
output: trending_coins: list[str], volatility_analysis: dict[str, float], security_alerts: list[str]
